This folder contains data related to galaxies
associated with FRB science.  Both hosts and
foreground galaxies.


The script build_hosts.py is used to generate
or re-generate JSON files for FRB host galaxies.
Best run by developers only.

-------
Additional

Data beyond that which is incorporated
in build_hosts.py

Should be limited to published literature

-------
SDSS

-------
PRIMUS

To generate star-formation main sequence figures,
you will need to download the PRIMUS catalogs from here:
https://primus.ucsd.edu/version1.html

PRIMUS_2013_zcat_v1.fits
PRIMUS_2014_mass_v1.fits


